body: Okay, I think I know what is happening. In the generated lds scripts, `_tensorflow_wrap_toco.so` exports the required symbol because of `*tensorflow*` and not because of `init_tensorflow_wrap_toco` because the actual symbol started with an underscore: `_init_tensorflow_wrap_toco` . None of the patterns listed in the lds script match for `_wrap_conversion.so` and hence the symbol `_init_wrap_conversion` remains non-exposed.
